document.full_text: australian open champion novak djokovic outlasted roger federer 6-3, 3-6, 6-2 to stay undefeated this season and reach the bnp paribas open final while knocking the swiss star from the no. 2 spot in the world on saturday.
document.title: nadal, djokovic to meet in indian wells final
